abstract: Ms. Warren’s total lagged what several other Democratic presidential candidates received in the first quarter of the year, but she had a strong finish to the quarter.
snippet: Ms. Warren’s total lagged what several other Democratic presidential candidates received in the first quarter of the year, but she had a strong finish to the quarter.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Senator Elizabeth Warren of Massachusetts raised more than $6 million in the first quarter of the year, her campaign said on Wednesday, trailing some Democratic rivals but exceeding the campaign’s worst-case fears after some early fund-raising troubles and the departure of her finance director.

abstract: The food is so good at these six restaurants, you’d want to go even if their prices weren’t so low.
snippet: The food is so good at these six restaurants, you’d want to go even if their prices weren’t so low.
lead_paragraph: On a drizzly night in Paris, a crowd spilled out the door of Bouillon Julien and onto the slick sidewalk lining the rue du Faubourg Saint-Denis. The lure was a bargain-priced meal that promised to be surprising for both its quality and reasonable price: less than 20 euros, or about $23, for a three-course dinner with a glass of wine.

abstract: Senator Bernie Sanders reintroduced his Medicare for All Act on Wednesday in a choreographed event charged with the unmistakable presidential politics of 2020.
snippet: Senator Bernie Sanders reintroduced his Medicare for All Act on Wednesday in a choreographed event charged with the unmistakable presidential politics of 2020.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Senator Bernie Sanders stepped to the lectern on Wednesday, red-faced and rumpled as ever, with a placard screaming “Medicare for All,” and likened his quest for a government-run universal health plan to earlier movements for women’s rights, civil rights, workers’ rights and gay rights.

abstract: Financial ills and a federal investigation, just completed, have led to discord at the club, whose members have included entertainment industry legends.
snippet: Financial ills and a federal investigation, just completed, have led to discord at the club, whose members have included entertainment industry legends.
lead_paragraph: For decades, the Friars Club has been America’s temple of comedy, a fraternity of jokesters and others who relish the rimshot and proudly regard bad taste as a core virtue.

abstract: The former prosecutor has found new notoriety — and big ratings — with her ferocious harangues on behalf of an old friend, President Trump.
snippet: The former prosecutor has found new notoriety — and big ratings — with her ferocious harangues on behalf of an old friend, President Trump.
lead_paragraph: One evening in 1996, as the Yankees clinched their first World Series in 18 years, Donald J. Trump was presiding over a masquerade ball at his sprawling Westchester County estate.

abstract: Boom! Studios is giving retailers free copies of Angel, the Buffy the Vampire Slayer spinoff.
snippet: Boom! Studios is giving retailers free copies of Angel, the Buffy the Vampire Slayer spinoff.
lead_paragraph: When new comic books arrive in stores on April 17, retailers who ordered the latest issue of a Buffy comic will get a bonus: free copies of Issue No. 0 of Angel, a new series.
